The drive to push boundaries, to reach further and aim higher, has always defined the American story. 

@ElonMusk’s plan to launch unmanned @SpaceX missions to Mars beginning in 2026 is a powerful continuation of that tradition. 

As NASA prepares to return Americans to the Moon, this simultaneous move toward Mars by SpaceX is a message to the rest of the world that America’s courage, ingenuity, and drive to lead is stronger than ever, and strengthens the foundation of a future where America leads humanity’s growth beyond Earth.

